author: CNET
description:
Can the iPhone 17 Pro replace a cinema camera? CNET's Andrew Lanxon puts Apple’s newest Pro iPhone through the ultimate filmmaking test.

We shot our short film using a combination of the iPhone 17 Pro and its built-in lenses, alongside the Black Magic Pyxis 6K with a selection of Arles Prime and X-Tract Probe lenses from DZO film. Spoiler alert: pro cinema cameras aren't going away any time soon, but your iPhone can still be an extremely powerful camera on a real production.

Check out the full video on our YT for the side by side break down.  #iphone17pro #tech #cinematography #filmmaking #blackmagic
title: iPhone 17 Pro vs. Professional Cinema Camera: A Short Film

description:

We dive deep into the practical uses of AI in photography, the evolution of wearable tech, and why simple camera upgrades on the iPhone 17 are changing the game.
